# VC‚āô dimension of convex sets in ‚ĄĚ‚ĀŅ‚Āļ¬Ļ, ‚ĄĚ‚ĀŅ‚Āļ¬≤

In the literature it is known that every convex set in ‚ĄĚ¬≤ has VC dimension at most 3,
and there exists a convex set in ‚ĄĚ¬≥ with infinite VC dimension (even more strongly,
which shatters an infinite set).

